<br>
When:  Sunday the 5th of August<br>
Time: 11am Pacific, 1pm Easter (I think 7pm Euro)<br>
Where:  Meet at the Top of the PoG Tower, or if you do not know the way at the Zoneline of Kael In Wakening lands.  <br>
<br>
This Raid will only occur if we have the following<br>
<br>
AT LEAST 12 people 50+ with at least 1 55+ Chanter 1 55+ Monk who has experience pulling PoG and 1 Cleric with a Rez Stick. The rest of this group should be made up of no less then tanks per group, one more cleric and 1 shaman, all others can be filled in with what we can get.  <br>
<br>
I'd like to take up at least 24 people but will take no more then 30  If we have at least the 2 groups of 50+ people I will take One more group of people 47 to 50, but they will not be allowed to take spaces in the main two groups.  This Plane cane be handled with 2 full groups 50+ with only a little effort.  If we take the full 30 people, still only 6 people will be allowed between lvls of 47 and 50.  <br>
<br>
Loot Rules are simple, if you need it you are allowed to Roll on it.  Only one peice will be withheld from rolling and that is Stability Legs, the first that drop are awarded to Kaisersos for his efforts in helping many of this guild and other guilds in getting their epics and/or closer to it.  IF he wants to refuse the item that is fine with him, but not me.  You have earned this mate. So deal with it and like it.  If anybody has problems with this do not sign up.  All Lolf Freinds and allies are Welcome.  Pls Sign up on the LOLF MB at the following URL <br>
<br>
